237
00:18:21,967 --> 00:18:24,276
Can I ask you something?

238
00:18:25,327 --> 00:18:29,002
Do you believe in love,
the kind that lasts for ever?

239
00:18:31,007 --> 00:18:33,441
- I loved my mother.
- No.

240
00:18:33,527 --> 00:18:36,519
Everybody loves their mother.
Even people who hate them.

241
00:18:36,607 --> 00:18:39,440
The question is,
one man meant for one woman.

242
00:18:39,527 --> 00:18:41,961
But it is not an interesting question.

243
00:18:42,047 --> 00:18:45,483
It is the question of a little girl
who believes in fairy tales.

244
00:18:45,567 --> 00:18:47,558
No. It's an everyone question.

245
00:18:47,647 --> 00:18:53,279
Everybody thinks they have the answer
until one day... something happens.

246
00:18:53,367 --> 00:18:55,562
Something happened?

247
00:18:59,127 --> 00:19:01,118
I understand.

248
00:19:01,207 --> 00:19:05,678
One love for you would be like having
