249
00:19:05,767 --> 00:19:10,204
And you probably like to go out to a
different restaurant every chance you get.

250
00:19:11,247 --> 00:19:12,043
Careful.

251
00:19:12,127 --> 00:19:15,597
- What's that? Are you hiding something?
- I hide nothing.

252
00:19:15,687 --> 00:19:18,155
- Excuse me.
- I'm sorry.

253
00:19:18,247 --> 00:19:20,522
- No. I have to go again.
- Again?

254
00:20:33,287 --> 00:20:35,278
Why did you let me drink so much?

255
00:20:35,367 --> 00:20:38,484
