299
00:24:24,087 --> 00:24:25,725
And I took it.

300
00:24:25,807 --> 00:24:29,959
And if there is anything else
I can do to help, please let me know.

301
00:25:04,207 --> 00:25:06,198
You are American, no?

302
00:25:09,647 --> 00:25:12,400
- For the moment.
- Well, forgive me for intruding,

303
00:25:12,487 --> 00:25:15,559
but I saw you sitting here
looking a little sad.

304
00:25:15,647 --> 00:25:20,323
"Why should such a beautiful woman
look so sad?" I ask myself.

305
00:25:20,407 --> 00:25:24,844
- Have you got an hour?
- As a matter of fact... always.

306
00:25:26,727 --> 00:25:29,446
Let me help you to forget your sadness.

307
00:25:29,527 --> 00:25:32,803
And remember that you are in Paris,
city of love.

308
00:25:33,767 --> 00:25:36,122
- Can I ask you something?
- Of course.

309
00:25:36,327 --> 00:25:39,956
Can you urinate
with someone standing right behind you?

310
00:25:41,167 --> 00:25:43,601
I think I could manage it.

311
00:25:46,847 --> 00:25:49,441
Are you going to be the someone?

312
00:25:51,687 --> 00:25:54,520
